These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
Color: azure, purple, lavender, orange
Transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. Color:orange is on the left of Color:azure##1
2. Color:azure is on the right of Color:orange##1
3. Transport:car is on the far left or far right##3
4. Color:lavender is on the right of Transport:motorbike##1
5. Transport:roller is between Transport:car and Transport:motorbike##2
6. Color:orange == Transport:bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Color   | orange | azure     | lavender | purple |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
