1. Birthday:february is on the left of Hobby:dancing##1
2. Hobby:fishing is between Hobby:board-games and Birthday:october##2
3. Hobby:fishing is on the left or right of Hobby:dancing##3
4. Birthday:october is on the left or right of Birthday:february##3
5. Hobby:board-games is on the right of Hobby:collecting##1
6. Birthday:july is on the right of Birthday:may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | board-games | fishing | dancing  |
| Birthday   | may  | july   | february  | october |

